sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant GitHub as GitHub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Tekton as Tekton/Konflux<br/>CI Pipeline
    participant PyPI as PyPI / UBI Repos<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Quay as quay.io Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as rhods-operator
    participant Controller as odh-notebook-controller
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP mTLS
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Workbench as Workbench Container<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant DataSrc as User Data Sources<br/>Configurable

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Dev,Quay: Flow 1: Workbench Image Build and Deployment
        Dev->>GitHub: Push code changes<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Git credentials
        Tekton->>GitHub: Clone source repository<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Git auth secret
        Tekton->>PyPI: Install Python packages (pip/micropipenv)<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, No auth
        Note over Tekton: Multi-arch build<br/>x86_64, arm64
        Tekton->>Quay: Push built container images<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Registry credentials
        Operator->>Quay: Pull images via ImageStream<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Pull secret
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create StatefulSet for workbench<br/>HTTPS/6443, mTLS, ServiceAccount token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over User,DataSrc: Flow 2: User Workbench Session
        User->>Gateway: Access workbench URL<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.3, OAuth
        Gateway->>RBAC: Forward authenticated request<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS, Bearer token
        RBAC->>Workbench: Proxy to JupyterLab<br/>HTTP/8888, None (pod-local), None
        Note over Workbench: User works in<br/>JupyterLab/Code Server/RStudio
        Workbench->>DataSrc: Connect to databases/storage<br/>TCP/Configurable, User credentials
        Note over Workbench,DataSrc: PostgreSQL (5432), MongoDB (27017),<br/>MySQL (3306), S3 (443), Kafka (9092)
        DataSrc-->>Workbench: Query results / data
        Workbench-->>RBAC: Notebook response
        RBAC-->>Gateway: Proxied response
        Gateway-->>User: Rendered notebook UI
    end
